   "source": [
    "from spopt import MaxPHeuristic as MaxP\n",
    "import geopandas as gpd\n",
    "import libpysal\n",
    "import numpy as np"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "##### Mexican State Regional Income Clustering\n",
    "\n",
    "Cluster 32 Mexican states into the maximum number of regions such that each region as at least 5 states and homogeneity in per captia gross regional product over 1950-2000 is maximized."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 14,
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2021-01-13T18:42:10.736951Z",
     "start_time": "2021-01-13T18:42:10.483324Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "<AxesSubplot:>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 14,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 864x576 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "image/png": {
       "height": 431,
       "width": 713
      },
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "pth = libpysal.examples.get_path('mexicojoin.shp')\n",
    "mexico = gpd.read_file(pth)\n",
    "mexico.plot(column='AREA', figsize=(12,8), edgecolor='w')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2021-01-13T18:41:24.866095Z",
     "start_time": "2021-01-13T18:41:24.861655Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "['PCGDP1950', 'PCGDP1960', 'PCGDP1970', 'PCGDP1980', 'PCGDP1990', 'PCGDP2000']"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 5,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "attrs_name = [f'PCGDP{year}' for year in range(1950,2010, 10)]\n",
    "attrs_name"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2021-01-13T18:41:24.885243Z",
     "start_time": "2021-01-13T18:41:24.867777Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "w = libpysal.weights.Queen.from_dataframe(mexico)\n",
    "threshold = 5\n",
    "top_n = 2\n",
    "mexico['count'] = 1\n",
    "threshold_name = 'count'"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2021-01-13T18:41:25.171344Z",
     "start_time": "2021-01-13T18:41:24.887211Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "model = MaxP(mexico, w, attrs_name, threshold_name, threshold, top_n)\n",
    "model.solve()\n",
    "mexico['maxp_new'] = model.labels_"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2021-01-13T18:41:25.178027Z",
